//github.com/datalad/datalad/pull/1464.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/datalad/datalad/pull/1464.patch"}, "body": "This fixes direct mode failure of `3rd_party_analysis_workflow`.\r\n\r\nThe actual point is to better deal with branches, managed by annex (`annex/direct/my_branch`, `adjusted/my_branch(unlocked)`, etc.)\r\n\r\nAdditionally fixes our calls to `git-annex-init`, which used to kill tracking branch information in `.git/config` if we cloned from a repository in direct mode.\r\n\r\nAs a \"side-effect\" further improves direct mode build when run entirely (`DATALAD_REPO_DIRECT=1 nosetests -s -v datalad`), not just the modules `tests` and `support`.\r\nThis locally results for me in:\r\n\r\n`FAILED (SKIP=55, errors=33, failures=43)` on master\r\n`FAILED (SKIP=52, errors=36, failures=20)` on rf-returnvalues\r\n`FAILED (SKIP=52, errors=30, failures=23)` on this PR\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "mih", "id": 136479, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEzNjQ3OQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/136479?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih", "html_url": "https://github.com/mih", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/1464/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0